title: DC Transit 'Other' Bus Stops
name: DC Transit 'Other' Bus Stops
description:
Other Bus Stops. This dataset contains bus stops for other bus lines, created as part of the DC Geographic Information System (DC GIS) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies.

Data provided by several bus companies and organizations listed bus stops for public routes supplemental to WMATA bus lines.

Acknowledgment of the DC Geographic Information Systems Program (DC GIS).
